Class OnItemClickListenerWrapper

    • Constructor Detail

      • OnItemClickListenerWrapper

        public OnItemClickListenerWrapper(@Nullable
                                  OnClickListener listener,
                                  @NonNull
                                  ValidateableDialog dialog,
                                  int buttonType)
        Creates a new wrapper, which implements the interface OnItemClickListener in order to delegate the method calls to encapsulated listener of the type OnClickListener.
        Parameters:
        listener - The listener, which should be encapsulated by the wrapper, as an instance of the type OnClickListener or null, if no listener should be encapsulated
        dialog - The dialog, the listener should belong to, as an instance of the type ValidateableDialog. The dialog may not be null
        buttonType - The type of the button or list item, the listener belongs to, as an Integer value
